oacPingResultsTable.name: oacPingResultsTable
oacPingResultsTable.description: Defines the Ping Results Table for providing the capability of performing ping operations at a remote host. This table contains objects outside the scope of RFC2925. An entry is added to the oacPingResultsTable when an pingCtlEntry is started by successful transition of its pingCtlAdminStatus object to enabled(1). An entry is removed from the oaPingResultsTable when its corresponding pingCtlEntry is deleted.

oacPingResultsEntry.name: oacPingResultsEntry
oacPingResultsEntry.description: Defines an entry in the oacPingResultsTable. The oacPingResultsTable has the same indexing as the pingCtlTable in order for a oaPingResultsEntry to correspond to the pingCtlEntry that caused it to be created.

oacPingJitterSamples.name: oacPingJitterSamples
oacPingJitterSamples.description: Reflects the number of jitter samples taken, it is usually one less than pingResultsProbeResponses. If 0, then the values of oacPingResultsMinJitter, oacPingResultsMaxJitter and oacPingResultsAverageJitter are not valid.

oacPingResultsMinJitter.name: oacPingResultsMinJitter
oacPingResultsMinJitter.description: The minimum ping jitter value measured.

oacPingResultsMaxJitter.name: oacPingResultsMaxJitter
oacPingResultsMaxJitter.description: The maximum ping jitter value measured.

oacPingResultsAverageJitter.name: oacPingResultsAverageJitter
oacPingResultsAverageJitter.description: The average ping jitter value measured.

oacPingCompliance.name: oacPingCompliance
oacPingCompliance.description: The compliance statement for the ONEACCESS-PING-MIB.

oacPingGroup.name: oacPingGroup
oacPingGroup.description: The group of objects that comprise the OneAccess extensions to the remote ping capability in RFC2925.
